   "html": "<tbody><tr><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"07m.html\">一覧　（マ）</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td></tr></tbody>"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "off"
   },
   "html": "<span class=\"m_r\">エピソード 1</span>調査中。"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "hidden"
   },
   "html": "<a name=\"s1\"></a>\n<a href=\"#s1\">＝</a><a href=\"#h\">△</a><a href=\"#h\">◎</a><a href=\"#s2\">▽</a><a href=\"#s1\">＝</a>"
  },
  {
   "type": "timeline",
   "rows": [
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　大阪府出身。東京商工中学校卒業。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　三井物産支那修業生を経て同社上海支店員となる。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　支店長山本条太郎に重用され、<a href=\"../p/sonbun.html\">孫文</a>との提携、中国興業の設立に活躍。のち天津支店長。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　三井物産退社後、衆議院議員。政友会所属。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　<a href=\"../1927/tanaa_1.html\">田中（義）内閣</a>の外務政務次官となり、東方会議を主宰するなど事実上外相の役を務めた。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　軍部と結んで積極的な侵略政策を推進、民政党の幣原外交を攻撃。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　政党の没落とファシズムの台頭に大きな役割を果たす。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　<a href=\"../1931/inu_1.html\">犬養内閣</a>では書記官長に就任。その後、急死。"
      }
     ]
    }
   ]
  },
